{
  "stem": "1415.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I mean, throughout my stay, it was going day and night, but after-- especially after we left, it never stopped.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I mean, the-- the skies were so red, and burning red day and night.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "It just didn't make a difference whether it was night or day.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "The sky was-- the skies were afire.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "It was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I remember always looking up, and I had my own little dreams.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I used to like watch and see the clouds, and-- and it was like bodies were floating by-- I mean, in my head.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I remember those-- those-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] those clouds of red.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And the-- and the stench was so thick, it stuck to your body.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "You could never get rid of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "You would-- after a while, you didn't even know the difference, because this is the way it smelled, everything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "But you could almost touch it, because it was like-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] like if somebody poured glue over you or something.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "It was always-- you were always thick.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And-- and that's-- that's when the ovens were going day and night, and night to day, during that time [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] when we were taken away.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And we weren't very long in that little camp, because they took us-- after that, they took us to the Zigeunerlager, and to-- which was the Camp E.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And, just the children's block.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, the gypsy camp.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a lot of twins were brought in that gypsy camp, a lot of twins.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I remember, they were, like, coming in the morning, and taken away, and never coming back.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Very few ever came back.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
